name: White Horse Tote
description:
A super cute tote, perfect for shopping or just carting around your bits and pieces.  Has two shoulder straps, and is fully lined.  Lining is white, and outer fabric is a royal blue with black stripes.  It features a funky horse silhouette screen printed in white on the bottom left corner of the front.
Completely hand made in Western Australia.

name: Purple Deco/Paisley Tote
description:
A light lilac cotton tote, featuring a design motif reminiscent of vintage art-deco wallpaper patterns, screen-printed in silver.  Fully lined with a gorgeous purple/pink paisley.  A must for the vintage lover.
Fully handmade in Western Australia.

name: Retro Blue/Green Flower Tote
description:
Groovy retro cotton tote, made out of genuine 70s vintage fabric.  Features an awesome pattern of flowers in a variety of blue/green tones, on a white background.  Fully lined in white cotton.
Completely handmade in Western Australia.

name: Cartoon/Orange Tote
description:
A bright, fun tote for the kid in everyone.  Outer in a knockout orange cotton, and lined with an awesome bright cartoon strip print cotton.
Fully handmade in Western Australia.
